          (unwind_backtrace) from [<8010bb34>] (show_stack+0x10/0x14)
          (show_stack) from [<8011ced8>] (__warn+0xf0/0x108)
          (__warn) from [<8011cf64>] (warn_slowpath_fmt+0x74/0xb8)
