          (debug_dma_unmap_page) from [<80601d68>] (dspi_release_dma+0x88/0x110)
          (dspi_release_dma) from [<80601e4c>] (dspi_shutdown+0x5c/0x80)
          (dspi_shutdown) from [<805845f8>] (device_shutdown+0x17c/0x220)
